<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV32">
<l>kurakkiṉappa ṭaikoṭuku raikaṭaliṉ mītupō</l>
<l>yarakkaraṅka raṅkaveñca ranturanta vātinī</l>
<l>irakkamaṇko ṭuttavaṟki rakkamoṉṟu miṉṟiyē</l>
<l>parakkavaitta ḷantukoṇṭa paṟpapāta ṉallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are the Primary Cause who went upon the roaring sea</l>
<l>Taking along the army of troops of monkeys, and shot cruel arrows</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the Rakshasas there were destroyed!</l>
<l>Are You not the Lord with lotus feet, which [You] placed extensively</l>
<l rend="indent">And measured for Yourself [the earth],</l>
<l>Without the least compassion for the man who gave [You] land as begged [by You]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
